high_descs: Turn left and walk to the trash can that is in between the sink and the toilet
Pick up the green spray bottle that is inside the trash can
Turn left and take a step then turn around to face the side of the toilet
Place the spray bottle on the back of the toilet in front of the candle stick
anns.task_desc: Place a spray bottle on the back of a toilet

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the spot between the sink and the toilet.
Pick up the green spray bottle that's in front of you.
Turn right and take a small step back.
Put the spray bottle on the back of the toilet
anns.task_desc: Put a spray bottle on the toilet.

high_descs: Turn left to face the trash can.
Pick up the spray bottle in the trash can.
Turn right to face the back of the toilet.
Place the spray bottle on the back of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: To move a spray bottle from the trash can to the back of the toilet.
